Load
====

29-Dec-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Translate strings in Options.xml, using the method in ROX-Filer.

16-Sep-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use new menu API.
Purge unused code and variables.

24-Mar-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added es translation (Juan Carlos Jimenez Garcia).

07-Mar-2006 (2.1.4)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added i18n support.

24-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added Zero Install injector feed.

16-Oct-2005 (2.1.3)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Can get ROX-CLib via 0launch.

12-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Update for ROX-CLib changes, many externally visible symbols
(functions and types) now have rox_ or ROX prefixes.

11-Sep-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Remove aclocal.m4, replace with rox-clib.m4 and aclocal -I .

27-May-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix for creating applets in remote mode, need to give the filer long enough
to notice the widget was created.
Use apsymbols for Linux portability.

31-Oct-2004 (2.1.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Update to new interfaces for infowin and choices.

2.1.1
-----
Don't use libgtop, it's not as portable as it seems.
Change to new libdir compilation system.
Changed some deprecated GTK+ functions.
Draw lines on the graph to indicate the levels.

2.1.0
-----
Get rid of some legacy code. 
Use ROX-CLib 2.1.0.
Stock icons in the menu.
Open options dialog from command line.

2.0.0
-----
Stable release to go with ROX-CLib 2.0.0.

1.5.2
-----
Italian translation of AppInfo provided by Yuri Bongiorno.
Safer way to parse ROX-CLib's version number by Christopher Arndt.

1.5.1
-----
Fixed text positioning.  Fix bug in displaying hostname.  Work on memory leak.
New icon provided by Geoff Youngs.

1.5.0
-----

Convert to GTK+ 2.  Switch to using options code from ROX-CLib.

1.4.1
-----
Fix compilation problems with paths with spaces.

1.4.0
-----
Stable release.

1.3.4
-----
Fixed bug in multiple window handling.

1.3.3
-----
Fix compilation problem with libxml2.

1.3.2
-----
Use replacement applet menu positioning code (from ROX-CLib).
Fix problem setting options for a window.

1.3.1
-----
Moved colour allocation to after read_choices().  Fixed bug in strip chart
if running multiple windows.

1.3.0
-----
Multiple windows.  Acts as a server, using SOAP, so there only needs to be
one instance running.

1.2.1
-----
Make sure AppRun can find rox_run.

1.2.0
-----
Stable release.

1.1.6
-----
Use new applet menu placement.

1.1.5
-----
Allow multiple strip charts.  Fix glich drawing red/green interface.

1.1.4
-----
Uses XML for config, if XML 2.4 or later.
Can select a font for display.

1.1.3
-----
Small changes to compilation system.

1.1.2
-----
Can change foreground & background colours as well.

1.1.1
-----
Create menu early to enable accelerators.
Time index the history so we can plot it right when the sample rate varies.
Bars now have slightly different shades.  Colours can be changed.
No longer check for changed config, not needed because of the applet menu.

1.1.0
-----
Switch to using ROX-CLib.  Option to display hostname.

1.0.0
-----
No changes.  This is the stable version.

0.1.10
------
Fixed bug in memory management.

0.1.9
-----
Don't scale down if the history is still big.  Support menu accelerators.
Run full screen version when applet clicked on.  Better debug output (uses 
g_logv).

0.1.8
-----
Allow user to set initial size.

0.1.7
-----
If the display is wide enough, provide a strip chart.

0.1.6
-----
Use new AppInfo.xml file.

0.1.5
-----
Slight adjustment to the display (lighter green, better use of
vertical space when small).

0.1.4
-----
Got rid of some of the warning messages.

0.1.3
-----

Added configuration window to set update rate and whether to show max
value and/or individual values.
